column1: Baby Barnaby's////We each got something different
column2: I got the Breakfast Tacos with potatoes and fresh fruit. It normally comes with black beans but not a big fan so he gave me fruit instead at no extra charge! Soo nice. Anyways
column3: everything was delicious and very fresh. The best part was that is was so reasonable...all of that for only $6.50-holy moly.
